phdl.designer
Class PHDLAssignment

java.lang.Object
  phdl.designer.PHDLAssignment

public class PHDLAssignment
extends java.lang.Object

A class that models an assignment statement in PHDL. All assignments are made after the "begin" keyword in the PHDL file. Attribute and pin assignments are made within instances, and net assignments may occur on their own

Version:
0.1
Author:
Richard Black and Brad Riching
